      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEAR TO EXCEL (1) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 520m at this track beaten 0.8 lengths (29.93) behind Billy Ray's Girl in a Grade 5 on April 30. Boasts two wins from five starts out of this box. Rates highly and will give a great sight. POUND KEEPING (4) was a last start winner (29.65) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from four starts. Leading player again. PRIM AND PRETTY (2) box seated before sticking on well to finish 4 lengths away in second (26.32) at Bulli in a Grade 5 over 472m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Leading player again. CUMBRIA LAURA (7) was well supported last time but could only manage second (30.19), beaten 6 lengths. Overdue and is among the main hopes.",
